<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Rayan Fiver Blog | Design & Web Development</title>
  <meta
    name="description"
    content="A professional blog about design, web development, and creative projects by Rayan Fiver."
  />
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="style.css" />
</head>
<body>
  <header class="site-header">
    <div class="container nav-wrap">
      <a href="index.html" class="logo">Rayan Fiver</a>
      <nav class="main-nav">
        <a href="#articles">Articles</a>
        <a href="#about">About</a>
        <a href="#contact">Contact</a>
      </nav>
      <button class="menu-toggle" aria-label="Toggle menu">
        <span></span>
        <span></span>
        <span></span>
      </button>
    </div>
  </header>

  <main id="home">
    <section class="hero hero-main">
      <div class="container hero-banner">
        <div class="hero-main">
          <p class="eyebrow">Welcome to My Blog</p>
          <h1>Design & Web Development Insights</h1>
          <p class="subtitle">
            Exploring the intersection of design, user experience, and modern web technologies. Join me on my journey of creating beautiful and functional digital experiences.
          </p>
          <div class="hero-actions">
            <a href="#articles" class="btn btn-primary">Read Articles</a>
            <a href="#about" class="btn btn-secondary">Learn More</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="posts-section" id="articles">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="section-head">
          <h2>Latest Articles</h2>
          <p>Insights on design, development, and digital creativity.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="search-section">
          <label for="searchInput" class="search-label">Search articles:</label>
          <input 
            type="text" 
            id="searchInput" 
            class="search-input" 
            placeholder="Search by keyword..."
            aria-label="Search blog posts"
          />
        </div>

        <div class="post-grid post-list-layout" id="postGrid">
          <article class="post-card" data-search="web design responsive ui ux modern">
            <a href="post1.html" class="post-thumb-link" aria-label="Read web design article">
              <img class="post-thumb" src="https://picsum.photos/id/10/900/520" alt="Modern web design interface" loading="lazy" />
            </a>
            <div class="post-content">
              <div class="post-meta-top">
                <span class="badge">Web Design</span>
                <span>15 Apr 2026</span>
              </div>
              <h3>The Future of Responsive Web Design</h3>
              <p>Exploring modern approaches to creating adaptive interfaces that work seamlessly across all devices and screen sizes.</p>
              <div class="post-meta-bottom">
                <span>8 min read</span>
                <a href="post1.html" class="btn btn-secondary">Read More</a>
              </div>
            </div>
          </article>

          <article class="post-card" data-search="ui design principles color typography">
            <a href="post2.html" class="post-thumb-link" aria-label="Read UI design principles article">
              <img class="post-thumb" src="https://picsum.photos/id/180/900/520" alt="UI design principles and patterns" loading="lazy" />
            </a>
            <div class="post-content">
              <div class="post-meta-top">
                <span class="badge">Design Principles</span>
                <span>18 Apr 2026</span>
              </div>
              <h3>Essential UI Design Principles Every Designer Should Know</h3>
              <p>Deep dive into fundamental design principles including hierarchy, contrast, alignment, and how to apply them effectively.</p>
              <div class="post-meta-bottom">
                <span>10 min read</span>
                <a href="post2.html" class="btn btn-secondary">Read More</a>
              </div>
            </div>
          </article>

          <article class="post-card" data-search="web development javascript frontend tools">
            <a href="post3.html" class="post-thumb-link" aria-label="Read web development tools article">
              <img class="post-thumb" src="https://picsum.photos/id/200/900/520" alt="Web development tools and setup" loading="lazy" />
            </a>
            <div class="post-content">
              <div class="post-meta-top">
                <span class="badge">Development</span>
                <span>20 Apr 2026</span>
              </div>
              <h3>Essential Tools for Modern Web Development in 2026</h3>
              <p>A comprehensive guide to the best tools, frameworks, and workflows that can boost your productivity as a web developer.</p>
              <div class="post-meta-bottom">
                <span>12 min read</span>
                <a href="post3.html" class="btn btn-secondary">Read More</a>
              </div>
            </div>
          </article>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="about-section" id="about">
      <div class="container about-card about-simple">
        <h2>About Me</h2>
        <p>
          I'm Rayan Fiver, a passionate designer and web developer with a focus on creating beautiful, user-centered digital experiences. With expertise in both design and development, I bridge the gap between aesthetics and functionality.
        </p>
        <p>
          I believe in continuous learning and staying updated with the latest trends in design and web technologies. My goal is to help others understand the principles behind great design and effective web development.
        </p>
        <p>
          When I'm not designing or coding, you can find me exploring new design trends, contributing to open-source projects, or sharing knowledge with the community.
        </p>
        <p>GitHub: <a href="https://github.com/rayanfiver95-designcreate" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">github.com/rayanfiver95-designcreate</a></p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="newsletter" id="contact">
      <div class="container newsletter-wrap">
        <div>
          <h2>Get in Touch</h2>
          <p>Email: hello@rayanfiver.com</p>
          <p>Location: Digital Creative Space</p>
        </div>
        <form class="subscribe-form" id="subscribeForm">
          <input 
            type="email" 
            id="emailInput" 
            placeholder="your@email.com" 
            required 
            aria-label="Email address"
          />
          <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary">Send Message</button>
        </form>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

  <footer class="site-footer">
    <div class="container footer-grid">
      <p>© 2026 Rayan Fiver's Blog. All rights reserved.</p>
      <div class="social-links">
        <a href="https://github.com/rayanfiver95-designcreate" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">GitHub</a>
        <a href="#" aria-label="LinkedIn">LinkedIn</a>
        <a href="#" aria-label="Twitter">Twitter</a>
      </div>
      <div class="quick-links"></div>
    </div>
  </footer>

  <script src="script.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
